  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3, W-EP-04)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. Model Risk Level is set to 3. Thirteen credibility factors are considered; ten are assessed with requiredLevel and achievedLevel populated. Three factors — Model form, Model inputs, and Equivalency of input parameters — carry factorStatus 'not-assessed' with rationale citing scope limitations. Because MRL 3 exceeds the threshold above which all factors should be evaluated, the absence of these assessments materially weakens package credibility (W-EP-04). The overall decision is recorded as Accepted, masking the epistemic gap.",
