    "rationale": "The assessment team concluded that the ten assessed credibility factors, taken together, provide sufficient evidence to support the hemolysis prediction claim at MRL 3. Three factors (Model form, Model inputs, Equivalency of input parameters) remain not-assessed due to scope and resource constraints, but the team judged these gaps acceptable given the conservative safety margins applied to the hemolysis threshold. No formal risk escalation was triggered for the unassessed factors.",
